TextEng: Can I ask questions about who you are?
Me ask about who you am?
Could I ask you something about this tavern?
Text: 이 선술집에 대해 몇 가지 물어봐도 될까?

TextEng: Me ask something about this bar place?
Text: 나 여기 술집 뭐 좀 물어봐도 돼?

TextEng: I'll be leaving.
Me go now.
Who are you?
Who is you?
What are you doing here?
What you doing here?
What was that about the Bloodsailors?
What about Bloodsailors?
Do you know what is planned for downstairs?
Text: 아래층에서 무슨 일이 예정돼 있는지 알아?

TextEng: What happening downstairs?
Have you noticed anything odd around here?
Text: 이 근처에서 이상한 걸 본 적 있어?

TextEng: You seen strange stuff around here?
Back to the inn... anything strange?
Text: 여관 얘기로 돌아가서... 이상한 거 있나?

TextEng: Back to inn stuff. Anything strange here?
Text: 여관 얘기로 다시. 여기 이상한 거 있어?

TextEng: Why is that so bad? What's in Scurrd?
Text: 그게 왜 그렇게 나빠? 스커드에 뭐가 들어가 있는데?

TextEng: Why that bad? What in Scurrd stuff?
Text: 왜 그거 나빠? 스커드에 뭐 있어?

TextEng: Why not?
What not make sense?
The auction won't go ahead?
Auction not happening?
How do I get down there?
How me get down there?
Thanks. Er, how did you know all of this?
Text: 고마워. 음, 이걸 어떻게 다 안 거지?

TextEng: Thanks and stuff. Hey, how you know this, anyway?
Text: 고마워, 뭐 그런 거. 근데 이거 어떻게 아는 거야?
